{"tid":1790395,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動] 草木皆兵 - 反制藍尸報警手足被拉","createTime":"2019-12-20T03:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T03:25:20.000Z","uid":272189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"719384b1e6fc844611c83e101683b1673a8d45f3","tid":1790395,"uid":272189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:13:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1790191/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1790191/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n有手足因為藍尸報警搞到被人拉咗，然而，我諗到一個幾簡單既反制措施，好簡單<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無中生有，草木皆兵</span></span><br />\n我地知道班popo一聽到有後生仔搞事就會精蟲上腦咁衝出嚟捉人，咁我地如果「見到」某個「高危」地方可能有人搞事都報警既話，佢地咪好忙？所以我係度呼籲大家<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔好</span>增加佢地既工作量<br />\n<br />\n但係要班popo信個報案人既話而出嚟擾民，同時確保自己安全，有幾點要留意：<br />\n1. 中年或老年人先好做，popo唔會信後生仔把聲<br />\n2. 對話中不妨表露自己係藍絲，唔係講「我係藍絲」，而係講「班曱甴」呢種藍絲說話<br />\n3. 太空卡，唔多講<br />\n<br />\n至於其他野，我未諗到<br />\n<br />\n就住呢個方案，大家不妨先推上去，俾多啲人見到討論下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔第一次開po，屌輕力啲"},{"pid":"b9e3b458b3965ca29490ca36c2c283c629b1d9c4","tid":1790395,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d015c8fe41774cfb642a62c63f716c3a9438b6d2","tid":1790395,"uid":272189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:14:20.000Z","msg":"自己係P牌，推唔到啊~~~"},{"pid":"c2f91535e43e12f9eafde7d39e9ca547293a92b6","tid":1790395,"uid":272189,"like"